Survival Analysis Practical

Preface

Library

library(pacman)
p_load(haven, dplyr, psych, lubridate, knitr, ggplot2, survival, broom, survminer, mfp)

Dataset

Import dataset

WHASDS <- read_spss("whas500.sav")
WHASDS

Convert to categorical data

WHASDS2 <- WHASDS %>%
  mutate(gender = factor(gender,
                         labels = c("male", "female")),
         BMICat = cut(bmi, c(0, 20, 25, 30, 100),
                      labels = c("Underweight", "Normal", "Overweight", "Obese")),
         cvd = factor(cvd,
                      labels = c("No", "Yes")),
         AtrFib = factor(afb,
                         labels = c("No", "Yes")),
         CardioShock = factor(cvd,
                              labels = c("No", "Yes")),
         ConHeartCx = factor(chf,
                             labels = c("No", "Yes")),
         CompHeartBlock = factor(av3,
                                 labels = c("No", "Yes")),
         MIOrder = factor(miord,
                          labels = c("first", "recurrent")),
         MIType = factor(mitype,
                         labels = c("non Q-wave", "Q-wave")),
         DischargeStatus = factor(dstat,
                                  labels = c("alive", "dead")),
         FUpStatus = factor(fstat,
                            labels = c("alive", "dead"))) %>%
  select (id,
          FUpStatus, 
          age,
          gender,
          hr,
          sysbp,
          diasbp,
          bmi,
          BMICat,
          CardioShock,
          ConHeartCx,
          CompHeartBlock,
          MIOrder,
          MIType,
          admitdate,
          disdate,
          fdate,
          DischargeStatus)
WHASDS2

calculate duration

WHASDS2 <- WHASDS2 %>%
  mutate(dur = as.duration(WHASDS2$admitdate %--% WHASDS2$fdate),
         dur_year = dur/dyears(1)) %>%
  select (id,
          FUpStatus,
          dur_year,
          age,
          gender,
          hr,
          sysbp,
          diasbp,
          bmi,
          BMICat,
          CardioShock,
          ConHeartCx,
          CompHeartBlock,
          MIOrder,
          MIType,
          admitdate,
          disdate,
          fdate,
          DischargeStatus,
          dur)

Overall

KM Estimate

Overall_KM <- survfit(Surv(time = dur_year, FUpStatus == "dead") ~1,
                      data = WHASDS2,
                      type = "kaplan-meier")

Univariable

Univariable - Age

Cox Proportional Hazard

age_CPH <- coxph(Surv(time = dur_year, FUpStatus == "dead") ~age,
                 data = WHASDS2)
age_CPH
Call:
coxph(formula = Surv(time = dur_year, FUpStatus == "dead") ~ 
    age, data = WHASDS2)

age 0.066339  1.068589 0.006079 10.91 <2e-16
